<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Project Update</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #dc3545;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #dc3545;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #dc3545;
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .project-info {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .project-name {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #dc3545;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .reason-box {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .reason-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #856404;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .tips-box {
            background-color: #e7f3ff;
            border: 1px solid #b3d9ff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .tips-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #0056b3;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .tips-list {
            list-style-type: disc;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .tips-list li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        .footer {
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding-top: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .encouragement {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #155724;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="icon">📋</div>
            <h1>Project Decision Update</h1>
            <span class="badge">REQUIRES ACTION</span>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= firstName %>,</p>
            
            <p>We've completed the review of your project submission. Unfortunately, your project has been <strong style="color: #dc3545;">rejected</strong> at this time.</p>

            <div class="project-info">
                <div class="project-name"><%= projectName %></div>
                <div>Review Status: <strong>Rejected</strong></div>
            </div>

            <div class="reason-box">
                <div class="reason-label">Reason for Rejection:</div>
                <div><%= reason %></div>
            </div>

            <div class="encouragement">
                <strong>Don't give up!</strong> Many successful projects require multiple submissions. Use the feedback above to improve your project and resubmit.
            </div>

            <div class="tips-box">
                <div class="tips-title">Tips for Resubmission:</div>
                <ul class="tips-list">
                    <li>Carefully review the rejection reason provided above</li>
                    <li>Update your project description and details accordingly</li>
                    <li>Ensure all required information is complete and accurate</li>
                    <li>Add more details about your project goals and impact</li>
                    <li>Verify that your project complies with our community guidelines</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p>You can edit and resubmit your project using the button below.</p>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= resubmitUrl %>" class="cta-button">Edit & Resubmit Project</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have questions about this decision, please contact our support team.</p>
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> StellarAid. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p><small>This email was sent on <%= currentDate %></small></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
